sentences.sContent: Pisces is a water element. ruled by mystical neptune this sign is extremely receptive compassionate and other-directed .
sentences.sContent_eng: Pisces is a water element. ruled by mystical neptune this sign is extremely receptive compassionate and other-directed .
sentences.sCn: 双鱼座：鱼儿是水相星座。受神秘的海王星所控制。双鱼非常善于接纳，富有同情心，并且很为别人著想。

remMethod.val: other(别人) + direct(指挥) + ed → 受人支配的
